Robin Weaver https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robin_Weaver 0 Robin Weaver (born April 1970) is an English actress well known for playing the roles of Clara in The Muppet Christmas Carol and recurring character Pamela Cooper in the E4 sitcom The Inbetweeners and its feature-length films, The Inbetweeners Movie and The Inbetweeners 2. She has also appeared in several television adverts.
